# VEHICLE::SET_VEHICLE_AVOID_PLAYER_VEHICLE_RIOT_VAN_MISSION

## Summary
Tag this vehicle to avoid only the player vehicle. Only to be used for riot van mission

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle
